{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "z5-t0iebgmy",
    "category": "story",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z5_t0IebGmY",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Don't move. Give me everything you have.",
      "zh": "別動，把你所有的東西都給我。",
      "ja": "動かないで。持っているものを全部出して。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Day three is a nightmare. Do you want to see why?",
      "zh": "第三天真是場噩夢。你想知道為什麼嗎？",
      "ja": "三日目は悪夢だ。なぜか見たい？",
      "time": "00:00:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Don't move. Give me everything you have.",
      "zh": "別動，把你所有的東西都給我。",
      "ja": "動かないで。持っているものを全部出して。",
      "time": "00:00:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay. Okay.",
      "zh": "好，好。",
      "ja": "わかった。わかった。",
      "time": "00:00:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will do what you say. I will not turn around.",
      "zh": "我會照你說的做。我不會回頭。",
      "ja": "言う通りにする。振り返らない。",
      "time": "00:00:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Please tell me what to do.",
      "zh": "請告訴我該怎麼做。",
      "ja": "どうすればいいか教えて。",
      "time": "00:00:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Take out your wallet.",
      "zh": "把錢包拿出來。",
      "ja": "財布を出して。",
      "time": "00:00:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Slowly.",
      "zh": "慢慢來。",
      "ja": "ゆっくりね。",
      "time": "00:00:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't have a wallet, but I have cash in my left pocket.",
      "zh": "我沒有錢包，但左口袋有現金。",
      "ja": "財布はないけど、左のポケットに現金がある。",
      "time": "00:00:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And a card in my right pocket.",
      "zh": "右口袋有一張卡。",
      "ja": "右のポケットにカードがある。",
      "time": "00:00:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am moving slowly. You can see my hands.",
      "zh": "我動作很慢，你可以看到我的手。",
      "ja": "ゆっくり動いている。手が見えるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good. Move slowly. No tricks.",
      "zh": "很好，慢慢動。不要耍花招。",
      "ja": "いいよ。ゆっくり動いて。トリックはなし。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No tricks. Let's stay calm.",
      "zh": "不要耍花招。保持冷靜。",
      "ja": "トリックなし。落ち着こう。",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We can both be safe.",
      "zh": "我們都能安全。",
      "ja": "お互い安全でいられる。",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Count to five and don't turn around.",
      "zh": "數到五，不要回頭。",
      "ja": "五つ数えて、振り返らないで。",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One, two, three, four, five.",
      "zh": "一、二、三、四、五。",
      "ja": "いち、に、さん、し、ご。",
      "time": "00:00:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello? I want to report a robbery.",
      "zh": "你好？我想報案搶劫。",
      "ja": "もしもし？強盗を通報したい。",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I just finished talking to the police.",
      "zh": "我剛跟警察談完。",
      "ja": "警察と話し終えたところ。",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am okay.",
      "zh": "我沒事。",
      "ja": "大丈夫。",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is my third day traveling alone in New York.",
      "zh": "這是我在紐約獨自旅行的第三天。",
      "ja": "ニューヨークで一人旅をして三日目。",
      "time": "00:01:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I was just shopping.",
      "zh": "我剛剛在購物。",
      "ja": "買い物をしていた。",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And then that happened.",
      "zh": "然後就發生了那件事。",
      "ja": "そしてあれが起きた。",
      "time": "00:01:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It was really bad.",
      "zh": "真的很糟糕。",
      "ja": "本当にひどかった。",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I just want to go back to my car now.",
      "zh": "我現在只想回到我的車。",
      "ja": "今は車に戻りたい。",
      "time": "00:01:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sorry, my bad.",
      "zh": "抱歉，是我的錯。",
      "ja": "ごめん、私のミス。",
      "time": "00:01:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I didn't see you.",
      "zh": "我沒看到你。",
      "ja": "君に気づかなかった。",
      "time": "00:01:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is your coffee okay?",
      "zh": "你的咖啡還好嗎？",
      "ja": "コーヒーは大丈夫？",
      "time": "00:01:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, it's okay.",
      "zh": "嘿，沒關係。",
      "ja": "大丈夫だよ。",
      "time": "00:01:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's just coffee.",
      "zh": "只是咖啡而已。",
      "ja": "ただのコーヒーだよ。",
      "time": "00:01:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you okay? Do you live here?",
      "zh": "你還好嗎？你住在這裡嗎？",
      "ja": "大丈夫？ここに住んでるの？",
      "time": "00:01:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes. I live on the street for six months now.",
      "zh": "是的。我已經在街上住了六個月。",
      "ja": "はい。もう六ヶ月路上生活している。",
      "time": "00:01:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Six months. What happened?",
      "zh": "六個月。發生了什麼事？",
      "ja": "六ヶ月か。何があったの？",
      "time": "00:01:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I got divorced.",
      "zh": "我離婚了。",
      "ja": "離婚した。",
      "time": "00:01:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I gave her everything.",
      "zh": "我把一切都給了她。",
      "ja": "彼女に全てを渡した。",
      "time": "00:01:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "She kept the house and the kids.",
      "zh": "她留了房子和孩子。",
      "ja": "家と子供たちは彼女のものだ。",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I have to pay money every month.",
      "zh": "我每個月都得付錢。",
      "ja": "毎月お金を払わなければならない。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "$2,000.",
      "zh": "兩千美元。",
      "ja": "2000ドルだ。",
      "time": "00:01:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That is a lot.",
      "zh": "那真多。",
      "ja": "それは多いね。",
      "time": "00:02:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What did you do for work?",
      "zh": "你做什麼工作？",
      "ja": "仕事は何をしていたの？",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I had a small hardware store for 15 years online shopping came.",
      "zh": "我經營一家小五金店十五年，後來網購出現了。",
      "ja": "15年間小さな金物店を経営していた。オンラインショッピングが来て。",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My business went down.",
      "zh": "我的生意衰退了。",
      "ja": "商売が落ち込んだ。",
      "time": "00:02:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I tried everything, but I still failed.",
      "zh": "我試過所有方法，但還是失敗了。",
      "ja": "あらゆることを試したが、失敗した。",
      "time": "00:02:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I lost my store.",
      "zh": "我失去了我的店。",
      "ja": "店を失った。",
      "time": "00:02:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Then I lost my home.",
      "zh": "然後我失去了家。",
      "ja": "それから家も失った。",
      "time": "00:02:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So you cannot pay now?",
      "zh": "所以你現在付不起錢？",
      "ja": "今は払えないの？",
      "time": "00:02:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, I can't.",
      "zh": "不，我付不起。",
      "ja": "いいえ、払えない。",
      "time": "00:02:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The court warned me.",
      "zh": "法院警告我。",
      "ja": "裁判所に警告された。",
      "time": "00:02:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I may go to jail.",
      "zh": "我可能會進監獄。",
      "ja": "刑務所に行くかもしれない。",
      "time": "00:02:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So I chose the street.",
      "zh": "所以我選擇了街頭生活。",
      "ja": "だから路上生活を選んだ。",
      "time": "00:02:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is better than jail.",
      "zh": "這比坐牢好。",
      "ja": "刑務所よりはましだ。",
      "time": "00:02:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "At least I can see my kids.",
      "zh": "至少我還能見到我的孩子。",
      "ja": "少なくとも子供たちに会える。",
      "time": "00:02:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They visit me once a month.",
      "zh": "他們每月來看我一次。",
      "ja": "彼らは月に一度訪ねてくる。",
      "time": "00:02:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Here, take this.",
      "zh": "這個，拿去吧。",
      "ja": "これを受け取って。",
      "time": "00:02:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is not much.",
      "zh": "不多。",
      "ja": "多くはない。",
      "time": "00:02:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You can buy some food.",
      "zh": "你可以買點食物。",
      "ja": "食べ物を買えるよ。",
      "time": "00:02:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:02:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can't take it.",
      "zh": "我不能收下。",
      "ja": "受け取れない。",
      "time": "00:02:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You don't even know me.",
      "zh": "你甚至不認識我。",
      "ja": "君は私のことを知らない。",
      "time": "00:02:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Life can change very fast.",
      "zh": "人生可以變化得很快。",
      "ja": "人生はとても早く変わることがある。",
      "time": "00:02:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Today is you.",
      "zh": "今天是你。",
      "ja": "今日は君だ。",
      "time": "00:02:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Tomorrow can be me.",
      "zh": "明天可能是我。",
      "ja": "明日は私かもしれない。",
      "time": "00:03:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's okay.",
      "zh": "沒關係。",
      "ja": "大丈夫。",
      "time": "00:03:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Take it.",
      "zh": "收下吧。",
      "ja": "受け取って。",
      "time": "00:03:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:03:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Today was a long day.",
      "zh": "今天真是漫長的一天。",
      "ja": "今日は長い一日だった。",
      "time": "00:03:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "First, the robbery.",
      "zh": "首先是搶劫。",
      "ja": "まず、強盗。",
      "time": "00:03:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Then I met that homeless man.",
      "zh": "然後我遇到了那個無家可歸的人。",
      "ja": "それからあのホームレスに会った。",
      "time": "00:03:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "His story was very sad.",
      "zh": "他的故事很悲傷。",
      "ja": "彼の話はとても悲しかった。",
      "time": "00:03:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I feel tired.",
      "zh": "我感到疲倦。",
      "ja": "疲れた。",
      "time": "00:03:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I just want to go back to the hotel now.",
      "zh": "我現在只想回飯店。",
      "ja": "今はホテルに戻りたい。",
      "time": "00:03:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Someone is knocking on my window.",
      "zh": "有人敲我的窗戶。",
      "ja": "誰かが窓をノックしている。",
      "time": "00:03:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You can't stop here.",
      "zh": "你不能在這裡停車。",
      "ja": "ここに停まってはいけない。",
      "time": "00:03:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am just here for a moment.",
      "zh": "我只是暫停一下。",
      "ja": "ちょっとだけここにいるだけ。",
      "time": "00:03:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It will be quick.",
      "zh": "很快的。",
      "ja": "すぐ終わる。",
      "time": "00:03:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am still in the car.",
      "zh": "我還在車裡。",
      "ja": "まだ車の中にいる。",
      "time": "00:03:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It does not matter.",
      "zh": "沒關係。",
      "ja": "関係ない。",
      "time": "00:03:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is a red zone.",
      "zh": "這是紅色區域。",
      "ja": "ここは赤いゾーンだ。",
      "time": "00:03:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No stopping means no stopping.",
      "zh": "禁止停車就是禁止停車。",
      "ja": "停車禁止は停車禁止だ。",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Not for drop-off.",
      "zh": "不能下客。",
      "ja": "降車のためでもない。",
      "time": "00:03:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Not for pickup.",
      "zh": "不能接客。",
      "ja": "乗車のためでもない。",
      "time": "00:03:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Not for anything.",
      "zh": "什麼都不能停。",
      "ja": "何のためでもない。",
      "time": "00:03:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am sorry.",
      "zh": "抱歉。",
      "ja": "すみません。",
      "time": "00:03:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I did not know.",
      "zh": "我不知道。",
      "ja": "知らなかった。",
      "time": "00:03:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I thought it was okay for a second.",
      "zh": "我以為停一下沒關係。",
      "ja": "一瞬なら大丈夫だと思った。",
      "time": "00:03:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now you know.",
      "zh": "現在你知道了。",
      "ja": "今は知っているね。",
      "time": "00:03:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is not just a rule.",
      "zh": "這不只是規則。",
      "ja": "これはただのルールじゃない。",
      "time": "00:03:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is about safety.",
      "zh": "這關乎安全。",
      "ja": "安全のためだ。",
      "time": "00:04:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Red curb means no stopping.",
      "zh": "紅色路緣表示禁止停車。",
      "ja": "赤い縁石は停車禁止を意味する。",
      "time": "00:04:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No exceptions.",
      "zh": "沒有例外。",
      "ja": "例外はない。",
      "time": "00:04:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I understand.",
      "zh": "我明白了。",
      "ja": "わかりました。",
      "time": "00:04:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I did not want to break the law.",
      "zh": "我不想違法。",
      "ja": "法律を破りたくなかった。",
      "time": "00:04:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I just thought it was okay if I stayed in the car.",
      "zh": "我只是以為待在車裡沒關係。",
      "ja": "車にいるなら大丈夫だと思った。",
      "time": "00:04:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do fire trucks wait?",
      "zh": "消防車會等嗎？",
      "ja": "消防車は待つの？",
      "time": "00:04:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "If they cannot pass.",
      "zh": "如果他們過不去。",
      "ja": "通れなければ。",
      "time": "00:04:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Every second matters.",
      "zh": "每一秒都很重要。",
      "ja": "一秒一秒が大事だ。",
      "time": "00:04:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do you want to block a fire truck?",
      "zh": "你想阻擋消防車嗎？",
      "ja": "消防車を塞ぎたいの？",
      "time": "00:04:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No sir.",
      "zh": "不，先生。",
      "ja": "いいえ、先生。",
      "time": "00:04:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am really sorry.",
      "zh": "我真的很抱歉。",
      "ja": "本当にすみません。",
      "time": "00:04:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I did not mean to cause a problem.",
      "zh": "我不是故意造成麻煩。",
      "ja": "問題を起こすつもりはなかった。",
      "time": "00:04:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I understand.",
      "zh": "我明白。",
      "ja": "わかりました。",
      "time": "00:04:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But this is still a violation.",
      "zh": "但這仍然是違規。",
      "ja": "でもこれは違反だ。",
      "time": "00:04:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am giving you a ticket.",
      "zh": "我要開罰單給你。",
      "ja": "切符を切る。",
      "time": "00:04:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You have 21 days.",
      "zh": "你有21天。",
      "ja": "21日間ある。",
      "time": "00:04:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You can pay or can test it.",
      "zh": "你可以付錢或申訴。",
      "ja": "支払うか争うかできる。",
      "time": "00:04:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The instructions are on the back.",
      "zh": "說明在背面。",
      "ja": "説明は裏にある。",
      "time": "00:04:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can't believe this.",
      "zh": "我不敢相信。",
      "ja": "信じられない。",
      "time": "00:04:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is not just a ticket.",
      "zh": "這不只是罰單。",
      "ja": "これはただの切符じゃない。",
      "time": "00:04:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is my food money.",
      "zh": "這是我的食物錢。",
      "ja": "これは食費だ。",
      "time": "00:04:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is my gas money.",
      "zh": "這是我的油錢。",
      "ja": "これはガソリン代だ。",
      "time": "00:04:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Then think next time.",
      "zh": "那下次想清楚。",
      "ja": "次はよく考えな。",
      "time": "00:04:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Move your car.",
      "zh": "把車移開。",
      "ja": "車を動かせ。",
      "time": "00:05:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:05:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am driving now.",
      "zh": "我現在開車。",
      "ja": "今運転している。",
      "time": "00:05:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Today is too much.",
      "zh": "今天太多事了。",
      "ja": "今日はもうたくさんだ。",
      "time": "00:05:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am so tired.",
      "zh": "我好累。",
      "ja": "とても疲れた。",
      "time": "00:05:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I just want to go back.",
      "zh": "我只想回去。",
      "ja": "ただ帰りたい。",
      "time": "00:05:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait.",
      "zh": "等等。",
      "ja": "待って。",
      "time": "00:05:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What is that?",
      "zh": "那是什麼？",
      "ja": "あれは何？",
      "time": "00:05:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh no.",
      "zh": "喔不。",
      "ja": "ああ、いやだ。",
      "time": "00:05:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "There is an accident.",
      "zh": "發生車禍了。",
      "ja": "事故があった。",
      "time": "00:05:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I need to stop.",
      "zh": "我得停下來。",
      "ja": "止まらなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:05:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This looks bad.",
      "zh": "看起來很嚴重。",
      "ja": "ひどそうだ。",
      "time": "00:05:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I should call 911.",
      "zh": "我應該打911。",
      "ja": "911に電話しよう。",
      "time": "00:05:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "911.",
      "zh": "911。",
      "ja": "911。",
      "time": "00:05:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What is your emergency?",
      "zh": "請問緊急狀況是什麼？",
      "ja": "緊急事態は何ですか？",
      "time": "00:05:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi.",
      "zh": "你好。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:05:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I just saw a car accident.",
      "zh": "我剛看到一場車禍。",
      "ja": "車の事故を見た。",
      "time": "00:05:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Two cars crashed.",
      "zh": "兩輛車相撞了。",
      "ja": "二台の車が衝突した。",
      "time": "00:05:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It looks serious.",
      "zh": "看起來很嚴重。",
      "ja": "深刻そうだ。",
      "time": "00:05:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:05:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What is your name?",
      "zh": "你叫什麼名字？",
      "ja": "名前は？",
      "time": "00:05:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Where are you?",
      "zh": "你在哪裡？",
      "ja": "どこにいる？",
      "time": "00:05:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My name is Maya.",
      "zh": "我叫瑪雅。",
      "ja": "私の名前はマヤ。",
      "time": "00:05:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am on Apple Street.",
      "zh": "我在蘋果街。",
      "ja": "アップルストリートにいる。",
      "time": "00:05:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Across from Cherry Park.",
      "zh": "在櫻桃公園對面。",
      "ja": "チェリーパークの向かい側。",
      "time": "00:05:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:05:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do you see anyone hurt?",
      "zh": "你看到有人受傷嗎？",
      "ja": "誰か怪我してる？",
      "time": "00:05:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "有。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:05:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One driver looks hurt.",
      "zh": "有一位司機看起來受傷了。",
      "ja": "一人の運転手が怪我をしているようだ。",
      "time": "00:05:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The airbag opened.",
      "zh": "安全氣囊彈開了。",
      "ja": "エアバッグが開いた。",
      "time": "00:05:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Some people are helping.",
      "zh": "有人在幫忙。",
      "ja": "何人かが助けている。",
      "time": "00:05:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:05:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Stay at a safe distance.",
      "zh": "保持安全距離。",
      "ja": "安全な距離を保って。",
      "time": "00:05:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do not move anyone unless they are in danger.",
      "zh": "除非有人有危險，否則不要移動他們。",
      "ja": "危険でない限り誰も動かさないで。",
      "time": "00:06:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are the cars blocking the road?",
      "zh": "車輛擋住路了嗎？",
      "ja": "車は道を塞いでいる？",
      "time": "00:06:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:06:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They are in the middle of the street.",
      "zh": "他們在街道中央。",
      "ja": "道の真ん中にいる。",
      "time": "00:06:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "There is more traffic now.",
      "zh": "現在交通變多了。",
      "ja": "今は交通量が増えている。",
      "time": "00:06:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:06:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Police and ambulance are coming.",
      "zh": "警察和救護車正在來。",
      "ja": "警察と救急車が来ている。",
      "time": "00:06:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They will arrive soon.",
      "zh": "他們很快就會到。",
      "ja": "すぐに到着する。",
      "time": "00:06:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "If you can, stay nearby.",
      "zh": "如果可以，待在附近。",
      "ja": "できれば近くにいて。",
      "time": "00:06:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But stay safe.",
      "zh": "但要保持安全。",
      "ja": "でも安全を保って。",
      "time": "00:06:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They may need you.",
      "zh": "他們可能需要你。",
      "ja": "彼らは君を必要とするかもしれない。",
      "time": "00:06:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:06:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will stay nearby.",
      "zh": "我會待在附近。",
      "ja": "近くにいる。",
      "time": "00:06:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:06:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We are waiting for the police.",
      "zh": "我們在等警察。",
      "ja": "警察を待っている。",
      "time": "00:06:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Finally.",
      "zh": "終於。",
      "ja": "やっと。",
      "time": "00:06:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Back at the hotel.",
      "zh": "回到飯店。",
      "ja": "ホテルに戻った。",
      "time": "00:06:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What a long day.",
      "zh": "真是漫長的一天。",
      "ja": "長い一日だった。",
      "time": "00:06:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't want to go out anymore.",
      "zh": "我不想再出門了。",
      "ja": "もう出かけたくない。",
      "time": "00:06:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm so hungry.",
      "zh": "我好餓。",
      "ja": "お腹がすいた。",
      "time": "00:06:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Need something to eat.",
      "zh": "需要吃點東西。",
      "ja": "何か食べ物が必要。",
      "time": "00:06:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うーん。",
      "time": "00:06:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:06:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll get pizza.",
      "zh": "我去訂披薩。",
      "ja": "ピザを頼もう。",
      "time": "00:06:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That sounds good.",
      "zh": "聽起來不錯。",
      "ja": "いいね。",
      "time": "00:06:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you for calling Johnny's Pizza.",
      "zh": "感謝致電Johnny's披薩。",
      "ja": "ジョニーズピザにお電話ありがとうございます。",
      "time": "00:06:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is Jack.",
      "zh": "我是Jack。",
      "ja": "ジャックです。",
      "time": "00:06:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How can I help?",
      "zh": "我能幫什麼忙？",
      "ja": "ご用件は？",
      "time": "00:06:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi.",
      "zh": "你好。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:06:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I want to order pizza.",
      "zh": "我想訂披薩。",
      "ja": "ピザを注文したい。",
      "time": "00:06:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sure.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "かしこまりました。",
      "time": "00:07:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What size would you like?",
      "zh": "你想要多大尺寸？",
      "ja": "サイズはどうしますか？",
      "time": "00:07:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A large please.",
      "zh": "請給我大號的。",
      "ja": "ラージサイズでお願いします。",
      "time": "00:07:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What toppings?",
      "zh": "要什麼配料？",
      "ja": "トッピングは？",
      "time": "00:07:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Pepperoni, mushrooms, and extra cheese.",
      "zh": "意大利辣香腸、蘑菇和加倍起司。",
      "ja": "ペパロニ、マッシュルーム、チーズ多めで。",
      "time": "00:07:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can I have thick crust?",
      "zh": "可以給我厚皮嗎？",
      "ja": "厚いクラストにできますか？",
      "time": "00:07:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We call it pan crust.",
      "zh": "我們叫它平底鍋皮。",
      "ja": "パンクラストと呼んでいる。",
      "time": "00:07:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do you want that?",
      "zh": "你要這個嗎？",
      "ja": "それにしますか？",
      "time": "00:07:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:07:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will take that.",
      "zh": "我要這個。",
      "ja": "それにします。",
      "time": "00:07:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do you want a drink?",
      "zh": "要飲料嗎？",
      "ja": "飲み物は？",
      "time": "00:07:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:07:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Two bottles of Coke.",
      "zh": "兩瓶可樂。",
      "ja": "コーラを二本。",
      "time": "00:07:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Got it.",
      "zh": "知道了。",
      "ja": "承知しました。",
      "time": "00:07:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Anything else?",
      "zh": "還要別的嗎？",
      "ja": "他に何か？",
      "time": "00:07:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's all.",
      "zh": "就這些。",
      "ja": "それだけです。",
      "time": "00:07:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかりました。",
      "time": "00:07:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let me repeat your order.",
      "zh": "讓我重複你的訂單。",
      "ja": "注文を繰り返します。",
      "time": "00:07:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One large pan crust pizza, pepperoni, mushrooms, extra cheese, and two bottles of Coke.",
      "zh": "一個大號平底鍋皮披薩，配意大利辣香腸、蘑菇、加倍起司，還有兩瓶可樂。",
      "ja": "ラージサイズのパンクラストピザ、ペパロニ、マッシュルーム、チーズ多め、コーラ二本。",
      "time": "00:07:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Your total is 28.99.",
      "zh": "總共28.99美元。",
      "ja": "合計は28.99ドルです。",
      "time": "00:07:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do you want to pay now?",
      "zh": "你想現在付錢嗎？",
      "ja": "今払いますか？",
      "time": "00:07:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Or when it arrives?",
      "zh": "還是等送到時付？",
      "ja": "届いた時に払いますか？",
      "time": "00:07:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will pay when it arrives.",
      "zh": "我等送到時付。",
      "ja": "届いた時に払います。",
      "time": "00:07:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can I have your name and address?",
      "zh": "可以告訴我你的名字和地址嗎？",
      "ja": "名前と住所を教えてください。",
      "time": "00:07:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My name is Maya.",
      "zh": "我叫瑪雅。",
      "ja": "私の名前はマヤです。",
      "time": "00:07:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかりました。",
      "time": "00:08:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます。",
      "time": "00:08:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Your order will arrive soon.",
      "zh": "你的訂單很快就會送達。",
      "ja": "注文はすぐに届きます。",
      "time": "00:08:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you for calling Johnny's Pizza.",
      "zh": "感謝致電Johnny's披薩。",
      "ja": "ジョニーズピザにお電話ありがとうございます。",
      "time": "00:08:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Done.",
      "zh": "完成了。",
      "ja": "終わった。",
      "time": "00:08:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now I wait for the food.",
      "zh": "現在我等食物送來。",
      "ja": "今は食べ物を待っている。",
      "time": "00:08:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh man.",
      "zh": "唉呀。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:08:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What a day.",
      "zh": "真是一天。",
      "ja": "なんて日だ。",
      "time": "00:08:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So tired.",
      "zh": "好累。",
      "ja": "とても疲れた。",
      "time": "00:08:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Today I met a robber.",
      "zh": "今天我遇到了一個搶劫犯。",
      "ja": "今日は強盗に会った。",
      "time": "00:08:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Then I met a homeless man.",
      "zh": "然後我遇到了一個無家可歸的人。",
      "ja": "それからホームレスに会った。",
      "time": "00:08:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Then the police.",
      "zh": "然後是警察。",
      "ja": "それから警察。",
      "time": "00:08:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A car accident?",
      "zh": "一場車禍？",
      "ja": "車の事故？",
      "time": "00:08:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wrong food.",
      "zh": "送錯食物。",
      "ja": "間違った食べ物。",
      "time": "00:08:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And that toilet.",
      "zh": "還有那個廁所。",
      "ja": "あのトイレも。",
      "time": "00:08:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Everything went wrong.",
      "zh": "一切都出錯了。",
      "ja": "全てがうまくいかなかった。",
      "time": "00:08:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But I am still here.",
      "zh": "但我還在這裡。",
      "ja": "でも私はまだここにいる。",
      "time": "00:08:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am safe.",
      "zh": "我很安全。",
      "ja": "安全だ。",
      "time": "00:08:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That is enough.",
      "zh": "這就足夠了。",
      "ja": "それで十分だ。",
      "time": "00:08:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Tomorrow is day four.",
      "zh": "明天是第四天。",
      "ja": "明日は四日目。",
      "time": "00:08:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I hope it is better.",
      "zh": "我希望會更好。",
      "ja": "もっと良くなるといいな。",
      "time": "00:08:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No more problems.",
      "zh": "不要再有問題了。",
      "ja": "もう問題はないように。",
      "time": "00:08:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Please.",
      "zh": "拜託了。",
      "ja": "お願い。",
      "time": "00:08:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good night.",
      "zh": "晚安。",
      "ja": "おやすみ。",
      "time": "00:08:47"
    }
  ]
